<section class="moment" id="moment">
  <div class="moment-inner">
    <div class="moment-mark reveal">Latent</div>
    <div class="moment-sub reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 80ms">The Moment</div>
    <h2 class="moment-heading reveal reveal-heading" style="--reveal-delay: 200ms">A photographer's journal, on iPhone.</h2>
    <p class="moment-body reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 300ms">
      The Ritual is for the photographs you sit with. The Moment is for the ones
      you catch in passing. Same engine, different instrument.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
